            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "About 10 gram of La2O3 powder of natural isotopic",
                " composition was pressed at 10 t/cm2 and a pellet",
                " 0.3 cm thick and 2.0 cm in diameter.",
                "The samples were placed at 0, 90 or 135 degree",
                " relative to the beam direction and centered about the",
                " T-Ti target at distances of around 3-5 cm."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "incident_source": [
                  "D-T"
                ],
                "reaction": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " An effective deuteron beam energy and beam",
                " current is 125 keV and 200 uA. T-Ti target was",
                " 2.40 mg/cm2 thick."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "HPGE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The crystal geometry is 70.1 x 72.3 mm in",
                " diameter and length. The relative efficiency is about",
                " 68%, and energy resolution is 1.69 keV at 1332 keV",
                " gamma ray from Co-60.",
                "The efficiency of the detector was pre-calibrated",
                " using various standard gamma sources, which were",
                " Mn-54, Co-57, Co-60, Cd-109, Ba-133, Cs-137, Eu-152,",
                " Am-241 and Ra-226."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "FISCH"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The neutron flux was monitored by a uranium",
                " fission chamber."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The irradiation was lasted 121 min with a",
                " yield around 3 to 4E10 n/s. The average neutron",
                " fluence rate in the place of the samples is around",
                " 0.95-3.54E8 n/(cm s)."
              ]
            }
          ],
